  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for ucode-intel",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\n  \nThis update for ucode-intel fixes the following issues:\n\nUpdate to Intel CPU Microcode version 20180108 (boo#1075262)\n\n- The pre-released microcode fixing some important security issues\n  is now officially published (and included in the added tarball).\n\nNew firmware updates since last version (20170707) are available for\nthese Intel processors:\n\n- IVT C0          (06-3e-04:ed) 428-\u0026gt;42a\n- SKL-U/Y D0      (06-4e-03:c0) ba-\u0026gt;c2\n- BDW-U/Y E/F     (06-3d-04:c0) 25-\u0026gt;28\n- HSW-ULT Cx/Dx   (06-45-01:72) 20-\u0026gt;21\n- Crystalwell Cx  (06-46-01:32) 17-\u0026gt;18\n- BDW-H E/G       (06-47-01:22) 17-\u0026gt;1b\n- HSX-EX E0       (06-3f-04:80) 0f-\u0026gt;10\n- SKL-H/S R0      (06-5e-03:36) ba-\u0026gt;c2\n- HSW Cx/Dx       (06-3c-03:32) 22-\u0026gt;23\n- HSX C0          (06-3f-02:6f) 3a-\u0026gt;3b\n- BDX-DE V0/V1    (06-56-02:10) 0f-\u0026gt;14\n- BDX-DE V2       (06-56-03:10) 700000d-\u0026gt;7000011\n- KBL-U/Y H0      (06-8e-09:c0) 62-\u0026gt;80\n- KBL Y0 / CFL D0 (06-8e-0a:c0) 70-\u0026gt;80\n- KBL-H/S B0      (06-9e-09:2a) 5e-\u0026gt;80\n- CFL U0          (06-9e-0a:22) 70-\u0026gt;80\n- CFL B0          (06-9e-0b:02) 72-\u0026gt;80\n- SKX H0          (06-55-04:b7) 2000035-\u0026gt;200003c\n- GLK B0          (06-7a-01:01) 1e-\u0026gt;22\n\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
